author: Jeffery Martin
title: Michigan Republicans Move to Clip Whitmer's WIngs in Battle Over Lockdown Extension
description: "We have work yet to do," Whitmer told MSNBC on Thursday while discussing the possible stay-at-home order extension. "We are still not out of the woods."
